Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.419 --> 00:00:06.410
COMM: Beefcake Arlindo de Souza super sized

00:00:06.410 --> 00:00:10.049
29-inch biceps are among the biggest in the
world.

00:00:10.049 --> 00:00:13.300
COMM: But they're actually fake, and the result

00:00:13.300 --> 00:00:18.289
of him pumping vast amounts of oil into his
body.

00:00:18.289 --> 00:00:24.800
COMM: The 43 -year-old is just one of a growing

00:00:24.800 --> 00:00:30.330
number of body conscious Brazilians, sculping
their muscles with a concoction of mineral

00:00:30.330 --> 00:00:32.519
oil, alcohol and anaesthetic.

00:00:32.519 --> 00:00:35.589
COMM: When injected, the mixture bulks up

00:00:35.589 --> 00:00:40.190
the body to give the impression of muscle
mass. but some enthusiasts in the bodybuilding

00:00:40.190 --> 00:00:47.190
world fear it can cause severe infections,
that result in amputations, or even death.

00:00:48.549 --> 00:00:55.549
COMM: The bodybuilder grew up in Olinda, worshipping

00:00:58.159 --> 00:01:04.140
Hollywood musclemen like Arnold Schwarzenegger.
He was already taking a cocktail of steroids

00:01:04.140 --> 00:01:11.140
when he was offered the muscle enhancing substance
at a gym two years ago.

00:01:12.200 --> 00:01:19.200
COMM: Arlindo injected it four times a week

00:01:23.679 --> 00:01:30.369
for two months, and the dramatic boost to
his body soon made him the talk of the town.

00:01:30.369 --> 00:01:37.369
His family were also shocked by his new look.

00:01:42.289 --> 00:01:49.289
COMM: Despite his burgeoning fame, Arlindo

00:01:50.200 --> 00:01:55.990
is concerned about the damage he has done
in his pursuit of perfection. Especially after

00:01:55.990 --> 00:01:57.420
the death of a close friend.

00:01:57.420 --> 00:02:01.429
COMM: His name is Paulinho. He was my friend.

00:02:01.429 --> 00:02:08.429
He passed away by doing these things. He went
beyond the limit. I've stopped the oil. But

00:02:09.479 --> 00:02:11.510
I have a desire to start again.

00:02:11.510 --> 00:02:14.209
COMM: Even though Arlindo warns against using

00:02:14.209 --> 00:02:20.370
oil, he is more than happy in his super sized
body. And determined to enjoy whatever attention

00:02:20.370 --> 00:02:27.370
it brings.

